			"id": 124338,
			"text": "xhorak: couldn't make firefox-40.0-4.fc22 crash on f22 (possibly didn't try hard\nenough), especially no scrolling issues with the cairo-gtk3 build at all â even\nwith \"layers.offmainthreadcomposition.enabled\" set to \"true\" and firefox\nrestarted. Meanwhile on f21, the stock cairo-gtk2 build gets literally unusable\nwith OMTC deliberately enabled due to the broken scrolling / repaint issues.",
